Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, July 25 (Reporter Yu Junjie, Chen Aiping) reporter learned from the State Internet Information Office on the 25th, 2020 App illegal collection and illegal use of personal information governance work was officially launched in recent days, focusing on combating the App background private upload personal information and other issues strongly reflected by the public.
