Chongqing, July 26 (Xinhua Han Lu) reporter learned from China Railway Chengdu Bureau Group Co., Ltd. on the 26th, the total length of about 18.9 kilometers of Zhengwan high-speed railway Xiaosanxia tunnel was opened on the same day.
It is understood that the small three gorges tunnel is not only the longest high-speed railway tunnel within the Three Gorges reservoir area, but also the longest single-hole double-line high-speed railway tunnel with a design speed of 350 km/h among the projects currently under construction in China.
Zhengwan High Speed Railway is located in Henan, Hubei and Chongqing provinces, connecting Beijing-Guangzhou and Xulan High Speed Railway in Zhengzhou, and arriving at Chongqing with Yuwan High Speed Railway in Wanzhou, which is an important part of China's "eight vertical and eight horizontal" high-speed railroad network along the river channel and Huanan Pass.
Zhengwan high-speed railway small three gorges tunnel 26 full line through.
The picture shows the completion site.
Zheng Wan high-speed railway starts in Zhengzhou City, Henan Province, southwest through Pingdingshan City, Nanyang City, Hubei Province, Xiangyang City to Chongqing Wanzhou District, the new line length of about 818 kilometers, the design speed of 350 km / h, about 184 kilometers in Chongqing.
Among them, Zhengzhou to Xiangyang section has been first opened for operation on December 1, 2019, Chongqing section is stepping up the construction.
The 26th full line through the small three gorges tunnel for Zheng Wan high-speed railway line control project, the project is located in Chongqing Fengjie County and Wushan County junction, the total length of about 18.9 kilometers, the maximum depth of burial 890 meters.
The tunnel started construction in February 2017 and will be fully completed on July 26, 2020.
According to the survey and design party China Railway Second Institute Engineering Group Limited Liability Company Zhengwan high-speed railway tunnel design responsible person Wang Guojun, small three gorges tunnel is located in the location of the terrain and geological conditions are very complex, facing karst, sudden mud and water, soft rock deformation and other risks, is a class I high-risk tunnel, tunnel design and construction is extremely difficult.
"During the construction of the project, we used geological survey method, physical prospecting method and over-the-top drilling method for over-the-top geological forecasting, and adopted special design solutions for more than 30 caves of various types. For example, a 24-meter-long bridge was designed and built to span large caves with a longitudinal length of more than 10 meters and a depth of more than 55 meters in the tunnel to avoid tunnel subsidence." Wang Guojun said.
According to the construction side of the China Railway Tunnelling Bureau, the tunnel construction, take the combination of dredging and plugging, through the construction of horizontal cave level guide, slurry plugging, strengthening the tunnel structure support and the construction of sewage treatment station, not only to ensure the orderly progress of the project, but also to avoid the construction of drainage damage to the water bodies of the Little Three Gorges scenic area, while successfully overcome up to 7 kilometers of soft rock deformation and other adverse geological, the maximum daily water surge of 15.7 At the same time, it successfully overcame the construction difficulties such as 7 km-long soft rock deformation and other adverse geology, and the maximum daily water surge of 15.7 million cubic meters.
Zheng Wan high-speed railway line is completed and opened to traffic, will become China's southwest region to the Central Plains, North China, the northeast region of the new convenient fast passenger transport main channel, to improve the capacity and quality of the northeast railroad channel in the southwest region, improve the layout of the regional road network, accelerate the development of tourism resources along the line and urbanization process, promote regional coordinated development, promote the implementation of the Western Development Strategy is of great significance.
