In the first two months of this year, the surveyed unemployment rate increased.
Especially in February, many enterprises' production and operation activities were basically in a state of shutdown and production suspension, which led to a decrease in enterprises' demand for labor, delayed or cancelled recruitment, and an increase in the urban survey unemployment rate.
With the gradual improvement of the epidemic prevention and control situation, the order of production and life in the whole society has been restored.
The Party Central Committee adhered to the general keynote of seeking progress in a stable manner, further increased macro policy hedging, comprehensively strengthened the employment priority policy and actively promoted the work of supporting enterprises to stabilize and expand employment.
